data.description: Discover the perfect blend of charm and modern convenience in this updated home. With a new roof (2019) and a complete HVAC system installed in April 2023, this residence offers both style and functionality. New flooring enhances the interior, leading to a welcoming covered porch. Situated on a double lot with a fenced yard, this property provides privacy and security. Close to schools and shopping. Don't miss the chance to make this your home, where modern comforts and a prime location come together for an ideal living experience.
